      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks, while the transmission shifts harshly. The exterior has several large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust spots, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functioning electronics. This is a project car or potential parts donor, sold strictly as-is.",
