    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, showing virtually no signs of wear and reflecting the highest level of pride in ownership. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior, every detail confirms its status as a premier example of its class. For the buyer who demands uncompromising quality and mechanical excellence, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience and lasting value.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
